<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.2">
<l>maṇṇiṭan tēṉa māki māvali valito laippāṉ</l>
<l>viṇṇavar vēṇṭac ceṉṟu vēḷviyil kuṟaiyi rantāy</l>
<l>tuṇṇeṉa māṟṟār tammait tolaittavar nāṅkai mēya</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉē kāva ḷantaṇ pāṭiyāy kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having [once] become a boar digging up the earth, you who begged in want,</l>
<l>Arriving at the sacrifice, as the celestials desired, to destroy Māvali’s power,</l>
<l>Kaṇṇaṉ who dwells in Nāṅkai where are those</l>
<l rend="indent">who destroy their enemies quickly,</l>
<l>You of the cool hamlet of Kāvaḷam, only you are [our] refuge!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
